rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0001
rows.name:
In the city of Torigo, I serve as
the representative of the Gulan
people... the Chief, so to speak.

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought it was just a title
until now, but since Morph was
demoted, I've been terribly busy.

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0003
rows.name:
In the old days, we would hold
discussions centered on the High Chief
and decide on Gula's policies, but...

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Since we came under Superbia's
rule, they hold the real power in
political and military affairs.

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0005
rows.name:
That kind of know-how was never
passed down to us Gulan people.

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Even if it's only temporary,
governing the city is truly
a difficult task...

rows.label: tlk41700321_03_msg0007
rows.name:
I thought that man Morph was a
good-for-nothing consul, but maybe
he was actually quite skilled.
